      "path": "audio/narrations/power-iteration/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "其中有一个最强的方向，对应绝对值最大的特征值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-iteration",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
