      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "于是向量会越来越偏向那个最强的主特征向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-iteration",
      "section_id": "normalize",
      "line_id": "norm-1",
      "filename": "normalize-norm-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-iteration/yunxi/normalize-norm-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.03,
      "size": 32544,
      "text": "光是相乘，向量长度会爆炸增长或缩到极小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-iteration",
      "section_id": "normalize",
