      "path": "audio/narrations/power-iteration/yunxi/normalize-norm-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "所以每一步都把它除以自身长度，重新缩回单位圆上。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-iteration",
      "section_id": "normalize",
      "line_id": "norm-3",
      "filename": "normalize-norm-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/power-iteration/yunxi/normalize-norm-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "这样我们只关心方向，方向才是真正收敛的东西。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "power-iteration",
      "section_id": "converge",
